official_title: A bill to designate certain lands in the Brigantine National Wildlife Refuge, Atlantic, Burlington, Ocean Counties, N.J., as wilderness.

summary.text: Designates specified lands in the Brigantine National Wildlife Refuge in Atlantic, Burlington, Ocean Counties, New Jersey, as wilderness in accordance with the Wilderness Act.
